++  poke-pass-through
  |=  [host=ship action=player-action]
  ^-  card
  ::  give a poke from frontend to host
  :*  %pass   /table-poke
      %agent  [host %pokur-host]
      %poke   %pokur-player-action  !>(action)
  ==
